{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 170°C. Line a large baking tray with paper towels then place chickpeas on tray. Shake tray so that chickpeas drain on paper towels.","Place cumin, paprika, salt, pepper and 1½ Tbsp oil in a small bowl. Leaving chickpeas on tray, remove paper towels then drizzle oil mixture over chickpeas. Toss until completely covered, then roast in oven for 20 minutes (170°C). Remove from oven and set aside to cool.","Place cavolo nero and 1 Tbsp oil in mixing bowl then with aid of spatula chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to a serving bowl.","Place garlic in mixing bowl then chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>.","Add sun-dried tomatoes, lemon juice, vinegar, coriander, mint, spring onions and chilli sauce, then chop <b>2 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to serving bowl.","When ready to serve, add cooled, roasted chickpeas to serving bowl then stir to combine."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["400 g cooked chickpeas, rinsed (drained weight)","½ tsp ground cumin","1 tsp smoked paprika","½ tsp fine sea salt","½ tsp ground black pepper","2 ½ Tbsp olive oil","200 g cavolo nero, stalks removed, cut in pieces (10 cm)","1 garlic clove","80 g sun-dried tomatoes","20 g lemon juice","20 g red wine vinegar","10 g fresh coriander, leaves only","10 g fresh mint, leaves only","4 spring onions, cut in pieces (2 cm)","½ tsp chilli sauce"]}],"id":"r222068","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-Fvc9wRQqJug\/XZMuqwFPEKI\/AAAAAAAAaIQ\/2fnGVEnqPWYIMR7rOPpXDmhDtUqz5QMbQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_OggzyIg9uqsmM7_t.png","title":"Cavolo Nero and Roasted Chickpea Salad","publishedAt":"2018-04-16T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"6.8 g","fat":"5.8 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"20.5 g","calories":"785 kJ \/ 187 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large baking tray, paper towels, serving bowl, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Lacinato kale, Tuscan kale, cavolo nero or dinosaur kale will all work in this recipe.","Leave to sit for <b>30 minutes<b> for flavours to develop before serving."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","25m","4 portions"]}